--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Theme Package To Do List
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Make sure the graphics adapter object's 'text_color' attribute has been set to
  the correct theme text color before calling the ThemeCell 'paint' method.
  
- Make sure the graphics adapter object's 'font' attribute has been set to the
  associated control's 'font' before calling the ThemeCell 'paint' method.
  
- Make sure the graphics adapter object's 'text_background_color' attribute has
  been set 'None' before calling the ThemeCell 'paint' method.

- Make sure the graphics adapter objects clipping region has been set to the
  ThemeCell's 'bounds' before calling the ThemeCell 'paint' method.
  
